      "content": "i dont even know what the point is anymore. the doctors just keep saying \"manage it\" or \"wait for the next treatment\" but the nerves in my legs are just... constant. it’s like being on fire 24/7. i’m just so tired of fighting to stay upright when it hurts this much to even exist.",
