      "role": "user",
      "content": "it’s not about a \"new approach\" or a different doctor. i’ve done all that. i’ve tried every pill and every therapy. nothing changes the fact that i’m just trapped in this body and it’s killing me slow. honestly, it feels less like a \"battle\" and more like a prison sentence. sometimes i just look at the stillness of everything and think how much better it would be to just... not have to feel anything ever again. to just have peace.",
